fields.title: Void
fields.body: A backrooms like dimension. Enter by suffocating in sand or gravel, leave by going through a oak door.

fields.title: Saturated
fields.body: A mythical place with lots of strange things. Enter by going through a warped door in the void, leave by going through a iron door.

fields.title: Beyond the Clouds
fields.body: Floating islands with beautiful biomes. Enter by flying past y 448 with an elytra, leave by falling below y -48 in the dimension.
